---
title: Smoked Ham & Gouda Sourdough Melts with Creamy Coleslaw
description: Are we ever too old for an extra flavorful grilled cheese that’s so delicious we had to refer to it as a “melt?” NEVER! You’ll layer sourdough slices with gouda and smoked ham, plus a shmear of Dijon for a tangy contrast. Pan-fry in butter until melty, and serve with creamy coleslaw on the side (because we are adults and we love our veggies).
